net.sourceforge.wurfl.core
Interface InternalDevice

All Known Subinterfaces:
Device
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultDevice
public interface InternalDevice

This interface represent an internal device instance, to be used internally for matching and caching purposes. Users are supposed to use and query instances of Device only.
